[I] A powerful tool for file type identification

[T] Supporting both signature-based and heuristic analysis, DiE enables
[T] efficient file inspections accross a broad range of platforms, including
[T] Windows, Linux and MacOS. It's adaptable, script-driven detection
[T] architecture makes it one of the most versatile tools in the field.

